{
  "text": "The DSC thermogram of drug and nanoparticles was shown in fig. 5 . In case of pure fenofibrate, a sharp endothermic peak was observed at 82\u00b0 corresponding to its melting point. In the drug-loaded nanoparticles, melting endotherm was observed at 80\u00b0 with sharp appearance. This change in slightly decreasing the temperature indicated reductions the crystallinity of fenofibrate in the formulation of nanoparticles [CITATION_1] .",
